Santi: &ldquo;Just before the semi-final against Atletico Madrid, I called Arsene and said, &lsquo;Boss, can I train at the Emirates just before the game?&rsquo;. The first thing he said was, &lsquo;You can play!&rsquo;. I said, &lsquo;No I can&rsquo;t play, only training my friend!&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Santi: &ldquo;If Arsene had stayed, maybe I would have stayed at Arsenal for one more year, but there were a lot of changes that year, a new coach [Unai Emery], new people working in the club, so I understood the possibility that I might have to leave.&rdquo;

